I know you feel distressed
about not playing tennis well.

52
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,720
I have the same problem.

53
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:32,760
There's a big gap
between my father and me.

54
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:37,960
You have frustrations, too.

55
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,080
Then let's...

56
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,120
Let's work hard together.

57
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:49,360
[laughs]

58
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,480
[sighs]

59
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:59,320
Whoa!

60
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:00,800
[chuckles]

61
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:02,960
Thank you so much.

62
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:04,920
Let's go.

63
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:07,240
You put all your effort
into beating your father.

64
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,240
Isn't it boring?

65
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,440
What do you mean, Uncle Jiang?

66
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:16,000
You can't beat him with only imitation.

67
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:20,279
It'll be good to have your own style.

68
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,160
[Ying] Uh, we forgot the cake.

69
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,440
-[Lu Xia] I'll get it.
-[gasps]

70
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,120
[chuckles]
Bye.

71
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,080
See you.

72
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:34,040
[school bell chiming]

73
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:36,240
Coach, I want to play against Lu Xia.

74
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,560
