have developed new theories.

80
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:53,440
Xinglong also progressed greatly.

81
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:56,120
All thanks to Lu Xia.

82
00:04:56,680 --> 00:05:00,440
So I also have an obligation
to help Lu Xia make a breakthrough.

83
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,840
I know how to inspire him.

84
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:04,960
[inhales]

85
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:07,120
Siyang, your hand got injured.

86
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:09,040
Lu Xia is no ordinary player.

87
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:12,360
-What if--
-Don't worry. I will be fine.

88
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:15,920
We can discuss it later.

89
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:18,280
The National Junior Tennis
is developing well.

90
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:23,560
Getting a good grade is important
for you to be a professional.

91
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:24,920
Exactly.

92
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:28,640
That's why I'm making the decision now.

93
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:33,040
[Siyang] Because it's also important
to Lu Xia.

94
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,400
[thwacks]

95
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,600
How is the racket?

96
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,680
