a piece of advice from him.

104
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,400
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

105
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:18,440
I don't know what he was talking about.

106
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:20,440
