[sighs]

156
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:00,920
[dramatic music]

157
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:04,800
[Siyang] Coach,
I want to play against Lu Xia.

158
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:07,960
I also have the obligation
to help Lu Xia make a breakthrough.

159
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:13,200
[Coach Qi] The most important thing
for him is not to be a copy of his father.

160
