[sighs]

162
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:23,400
[school bell chiming]

163
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,000
[indistinct chatter]

164
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:29,200
SIX DAYS BEFORE THE MUNICIPAL QUALIFYING

165
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:31,160
[student 3] Siyang is so handsome.

166
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,240
[Yung] Siyang.

167
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:34,000
[student 4] He's so tall.

168
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,560
Are you looking for Lu Xia?

169
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:38,760
[Siyang] Yes.

170
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,760
I'm leaving.

171
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:43,320
[student 3] He's perfect.

172
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:45,120
[student 4] He walks so gracefully.

173
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,280
[students giggling]

174
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,480
How can he be so perfect?

175
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,360
Lu Xia.

176
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,320
[Lu Xia] What's up?

177
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:02,280
I'll wait for you at the indoor court
at 3:00 p.m. three days from now.

178
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:07,240
[indistinct chatter]

179
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:11,120
[both laugh]

180
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,680
What did the captain say?

181
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:13,800
You look so happy.

182
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,920
Chi.

183
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,960
You want to have a private game with him?

184
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:26,480
[sighs deeply]

185
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:28,880
You heard it?

186
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,240
I was not sure.

187
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:35,520
-But then I saw you.
-Keep it a secret for me.

188
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:38,720
What are you thinking?

189
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:41,480
-[Dayong] Your arm got injured.
-I'm fine.

190
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:42,920
-But you--
-I'm fine.

191
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:48,000
Aren't you going to check
the freshmen's sanitary conditions?

192
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,560
Go.

193
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,240
But...

194
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:55,760
[Coach Qi] Lu Xia.

195
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:58,120
Did Siyang talk to you about the game?

196
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,560
Yes.

197
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:01,520
Is this your plan?

198
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,400
It's Siyang's proposal.

199
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,480
Siyang's proposal?

200
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,960
He'll do his best.

201
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:10,480
You'd better get ready.

202
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:14,040
He is better than all the opponents
you have faced before.

203
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:14,960
Really?

204
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:18,520
Let's just say,
he's not worse than your father.

205
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:23,160
He is even stronger than your father
when he was at his age.

206
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:27,160
Are you trying to provoke me?

207
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:28,600
[snickers]

208
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:35,280
Your elbow injury
hasn't recovered completely.

209
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:38,640
And you didn't stop practicing
these past few days.

210
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:43,680
It makes your starting tendon deform,
degenerate, and wear down.

211
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,320
Are you left-handed?

212
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,280
Yes.

213
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:53,800
Continuing high-intensity training
with your left hand

214
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:56,160
will cause inflammation
and pain in this area.

215
00:11:56,800 --> 00:11:59,160
Once you get the tennis elbow,

216
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:02,600
your career will die.

217
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:08,040
Doctor, do you mean he has
to continue the treatment?

218
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,760
The nationals are coming soon.

219
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:12,760
We can't win without him.

220
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:14,480
[snickers]
Let me finish.

221
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:17,080
Your rehabilitation is going well.

222
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:20,160
You will recover soon.

223
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:24,680
But you can't play
high-intensity games for now.

224
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:27,720
And you can't use your skillful chip.

225
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:31,280
Otherwise, all your efforts
will be in vain.

226
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:34,160
[somber music]

227
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:51,440
I'll wait for you at the indoor court
at 3:00 p.m. three days from now.

228
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,120
[chuckles]

229
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:56,080
Siyang.

230
00:12:57,880 --> 00:12:59,080
[cat meows]

231
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:11,680
FIVE DAYS BEFORE THE MUNICIPAL QUALIFYING

232
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,320
[Dayong sighs]

233
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:31,440
I can do basic training now.

234
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:34,160
-And--
-You heard the doctor,

235
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,920
and yet you still want
to play against him?

236
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:38,000
Yes.

237
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:39,760
He said my rehabilitation is going well.

238
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,880
So there won't be any problems.

239
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:43,600
-But you--
-Don't make me say it again.

240
00:13:45,880 --> 00:13:46,840
