241
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,160
[Dayong exhales sharply]

242
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:00,600
[sighs]

243
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:03,600
That's strange.

244
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,960
[Tang Jiale] The captain is practicing.

245
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:09,840
Is it for the upcoming
municipal qualifying?

246
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:13,480
Even our captain is nervous.

247
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:14,760
Yes.

248
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:16,680
The match is coming soon.

249
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:19,960
[chuckles]

250
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:25,240
[machine pops]

251
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:27,720
[upbeat music]

252
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:30,640
-[thwacking]
-[ball whooshing]

253
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:49,480
[ball thuds]

254
00:14:55,560 --> 00:14:59,520
THREE DAYS
BEFORE THE MUNICIPAL QUALIFYING

255
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:06,080
[inhales]

256
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:09,200
[grunting]

257
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:15,280
[sighing]

258
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:30,360
That's strange.

259
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:33,960
Only a few people are practicing today.

260
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,080
They skipped practice.

261
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:44,000
That's weird.

262
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:45,880
Even the captain didn't show up.

263
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:47,280
That's right.

264
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,120
Neither does Lu Xia.

265
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,320
[Tang Jiale] Nor Coach.

266
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:53,200
Even Chi is not here.

267
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,840
[Yan Zhiming] Lu Xia asked for sick leave.

268
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,360
How can he be sick?

269
00:16:04,920 --> 00:16:05,920
What about Siyang?

270
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:07,960
He's on sick leave, too.

271
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:12,280
What about Chi? Is he sick, too?

272
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:15,440
Seems like we can finally do
some reasoning.

273
00:16:16,880 --> 00:16:18,160
No way.

274
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:20,080
Why didn't he tell me?

275
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:23,760
-What does this have to do with reasoning?
-Of course.

276
00:16:24,920 --> 00:16:26,000
According to my reasoning,

277
00:16:26,400 --> 00:16:28,680
there's a hundred percent chance
that there's something...

278
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,400
secretly going on.

279
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:37,400
♪ I have missed so many sunsets
To seek the end and the truth ♪

280
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:38,640
♪ I couldn't see my front far enough
With only one or two steps ♪

281
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:39,800
♪ The peach blossoms
Diffused a fragrant smell in my dream ♪

282
00:16:39,880 --> 00:16:42,000
♪ I was stubborn
But couldn't defeat a deception ♪

283
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:43,200
♪ To find out the truth
In black and white ♪

284
00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:44,600
♪ I had to wait dawning ♪

285
00:16:44,680 --> 00:16:46,000
♪ Could I show my natural skills
With my own hands? ♪

286
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:47,240
♪ You drew your tri-point,
Double-edged sword from its sheath ♪

287
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:48,720
♪ The bodies of dragon, phoenix
And Kirin collapsed ♪

288
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:50,160
♪ The pieces of the jade stairs
Were flying all over as my cudgel waved ♪

289
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:51,240
♪ I had no more time to look back ♪

290
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,200
♪ The only thing
Was left between the leaves ♪

291
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:53,240
♪ And the earth in thousands of years is ♪

292
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,600
-♪ The bang ♪
-[Sha clears throat]

293
00:16:54,680 --> 00:16:55,760
[wood clatter]

294
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:57,080
You're early today.

295
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,240
You...

296
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:00,760
[Xiangqian gasps]

297
00:17:01,280 --> 00:17:02,280
It's you.

298
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:05,359
Excuse me, Mr. Lu.

299
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:06,839
Don't mind me.

300
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,480
Did you bring the toll?

301
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:10,640
Oh.

302
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:15,760
Whoa.

303
00:17:16,599 --> 00:17:17,560
[gasps]

304
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:19,359
Mr. Lu.

305
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:23,240
I came for our 20th-anniversary
special report.

306
00:17:23,319 --> 00:17:24,280
No problem.

307
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:25,760
[both chuckle]

308
00:17:28,359 --> 00:17:30,359
[tense music]

309
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:40,920
[tense music continues]

310
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:45,360
ADDRESSEE, LU XIANGQIAN

311
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:46,840
[Xiangqian] In those days,

312
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:50,840
high school tennis
was a lot less glorious.

313
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:54,920
Where should I start?

314
00:17:57,360 --> 00:17:59,040
[water trickling]

315
00:18:07,120 --> 00:18:08,040
This one.

316
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:11,800
This letter was big.

317
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:18,320
I remember
when I just became a main player.

318
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:20,600
I had a lot of admirers.

319
00:18:20,920 --> 00:18:22,000
No.

320
00:18:22,080 --> 00:18:23,680
[Sha] Mr. Lu.

321
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:28,400
The special report I talked about
is not like this.

322
00:18:28,800 --> 00:18:30,800
Then what is this?

323
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:32,760
I have a lot of experience.

324
00:18:33,320 --> 00:18:34,320
For example,

325
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:37,640
how did you start playing tennis?

326
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:40,120
Aren't you reporting
about the high school league?

327
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,880
So I'll start from my high school.

328
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:44,040
No, please start from your childhood.

329
00:18:44,120 --> 00:18:47,000
[Sha] The chief editor said
that I have to get a scoop on you

330
00:18:47,080 --> 00:18:49,560
or else I won't have the whole page
for the high school league.

331
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:50,720
Please.

332
00:18:53,560 --> 00:18:55,960
[sighs]
Okay.

333
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:00,400
When I was three years old,

334
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,680
my Uncle Toni

335
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:05,280
took me to the World of Tennis.

336
00:19:06,360 --> 00:19:08,160
Toni?

337
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:11,280
I was a right-hand player,

338
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:14,240
but I switched to left-hand

339
00:19:14,480 --> 00:19:16,760
-under my uncle's advice.
-Wait.

340
00:19:17,360 --> 00:19:20,200
Isn't that Nadal?

341
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:21,200
Don't interrupt.

342
00:19:22,280 --> 00:19:23,640
[Xiangqian] At school,

343
00:19:24,320 --> 00:19:26,240
I participated in two events.

344
00:19:27,280 --> 00:19:30,520
-One is tennis, the other is...
-Soccer.

345
00:19:31,040 --> 00:19:32,200
How did you know?

346
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:33,160
[chuckles]

347
00:19:34,120 --> 00:19:35,960
That's Federer.

348
00:19:36,520 --> 00:19:38,440
What should I talk about
when you know everything?

349
00:19:38,520 --> 00:19:39,520
It's boring.

350
00:19:39,600 --> 00:19:43,280
[Sha breathes deeply]

351
00:19:50,360 --> 00:19:52,360
[tense music]

352
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:05,360
Can we start?

353
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:13,320
[thwacks]

354
00:20:16,560 --> 00:20:17,600
[chuckles]

355
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:21,320
A fast ball at the beginning of a game.

356
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:32,040
[gasps]

357
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:39,840
[sighs sharply]

358
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,320
-[thwacks]
-[Siyang grunts]

359
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:45,840
[thwacking]

360
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:51,520
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

361
00:20:53,040 --> 00:20:56,120
[grunts, panting]

362
00:20:58,240 --> 00:20:59,880
[Dayong] Siyang is as fast as usual.

363
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:06,040
Can you still play?

364
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:09,080
[chuckles]

365
00:21:11,200 --> 00:21:12,520
[pants]

366
00:21:12,600 --> 00:21:14,360
Of course. I will win.

367
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:17,880
[upbeat music]

368
00:21:30,520 --> 00:21:32,520
[upbeat music continues]

369
00:21:35,320 --> 00:21:36,400
-[thwacks]
-[ball whooshes]

370
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:43,480
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

371
00:21:51,240 --> 00:21:52,320
[Lu Xia gasps]

372
00:21:56,200 --> 00:21:57,760
Do you still think you can win?

373
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:01,800
[Lu Xia panting]

374
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,640
[action music]

375
00:22:09,840 --> 00:22:10,840
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

376
00:22:27,280 --> 00:22:28,640
[thwacking]

377
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:30,600
[grunts]

378
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:33,640
-[thwacking]
-[ball thumping]

379
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:38,600
[Lu Xia pants]

380
00:22:42,520 --> 00:22:43,560
[grunting]

381
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,520
[groaning]

382
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:49,960
-[grunts]
-[thwacks]

383
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,280
[gasps]

384
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:57,080
-[thwacking]
-[grunts]

385
00:22:59,840 --> 00:23:00,760
[groans]

386
00:23:06,320 --> 00:23:10,480
[Dayong] Even a double-volley
with a split step can't threaten Siyang.

387
00:23:13,120 --> 00:23:14,160
[Siyang] Lu Xia.

388
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:17,200
Why do you play tennis?

389
00:23:17,800 --> 00:23:18,800
I have a goal.

390
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,320
What's your goal?

391
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:26,200
A man.

392
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:29,520
Your goal is to just beat a man?

393
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:32,360
That's not a good reason.

394
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:34,680
[panting]

395
00:23:35,560 --> 00:23:36,880
[snickers]

396
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:38,000
What's your point?

397
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:41,480
What will you do after beating him?

398
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:45,000
What will you gain after that?

399
00:23:49,800 --> 00:23:51,680
[panting]

400
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:53,280
Before thinking about that,

401
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:56,720
all I want is to focus...

402
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:02,200
[action music]

403
00:24:08,520 --> 00:24:09,960
...and beat you.

404
00:24:11,960 --> 00:24:12,920
[Dayong] Zero-chip?

405
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:17,160
[doctor] You can't play
high-intensity games for now.

406
00:24:17,640 --> 00:24:20,320
And you can't use your skillful chip.

407
00:24:21,080 --> 00:24:22,000
Siyang, no!

408
00:24:22,080 --> 00:24:24,120
[ball whooshing]

409
00:24:26,360 --> 00:24:27,240
[Siyang grunts]

410
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:30,040
ZERO-CHIP

411
00:24:34,960 --> 00:24:35,800
[grunts]

412
00:24:42,560 --> 00:24:44,560
[upbeat music]

413
00:24:51,040 --> 00:24:52,520
Aren't you going to beat me?

414
00:24:59,560 --> 00:25:00,760
[Siyang] To win the game,

415
00:25:01,120 --> 00:25:02,680
you have to be stronger.

416
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:10,000
When you truly know
the reason you play tennis,

417
00:25:10,560 --> 00:25:12,720
you'll have the ability
to overcome the obstacles.

418
00:25:13,440 --> 00:25:15,640
You'll be stronger on the court.

419
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:18,200
[panting]

420
00:25:18,280 --> 00:25:19,200
Lu Xia.

421
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:21,720
Please be Yu Qing's pillar.

422
00:25:28,360 --> 00:25:30,960
[retreating footsteps]

423
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:44,280
[Sha] This is the ball you used
on your first nationals.

424
00:25:45,040 --> 00:25:47,200
-Where did you get it?
-Coach Qi gave it to me.

425
00:25:47,280 --> 00:25:48,800
[Xiangqian] You didn't make an effort.

426
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:52,480
[playful music]

427
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:55,280
Look.

428
00:25:55,760 --> 00:25:57,400
-Qi Na was beautiful and gentle
-Whoa.

429
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:59,640
when she was young.

430
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:01,040
Look at her now.

431
00:26:01,120 --> 00:26:03,520
She's too tough,
the kids are afraid of her.

432
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:07,840
Ah. You kept this, too?

433
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:09,680
I just put it there.

434
00:26:10,360 --> 00:26:12,760
[Sha] I saw the game
between Yu Qing and Yu Feng.

435
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:15,280
Lu Xia looks like you when playing tennis.

436
00:26:15,360 --> 00:26:17,600
Especially when he was doing
the double-volley.

437
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:18,560
[clicks tongue]

438
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:21,640
I felt like I was watching your game
20 years ago.

439
00:26:31,560 --> 00:26:33,760
[Dayong] Captain, have a seat.

440
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:36,080
It's just a game.

441
00:26:36,360 --> 00:26:38,000
I'm not that tired.

442
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:42,000
Captain, it's not just a game.

443
00:26:42,320 --> 00:26:43,760
I've seen it all.

444
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:45,600
Why did you take such a risk?

445
00:26:45,680 --> 00:26:48,720
What if your injury gets worse?

446
00:26:49,520 --> 00:26:50,960
This game is meaningless

447
00:26:51,560 --> 00:26:53,840
if I didn't do so.

448
00:26:58,120 --> 00:27:01,200
That's all I can do for him.

449
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:03,720
[Dayong sighs]

450
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:09,520
Captain, do you think Lu Xia
will get back up?

451
00:27:10,560 --> 00:27:12,960
It's right to do so,

452
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:16,040
but he must be really frustrated.

453
00:27:17,120 --> 00:27:18,520
[chuckles]

454
00:27:18,600 --> 00:27:21,920
It seems that he has never lost
a game before.

455
00:27:23,280 --> 00:27:24,360
[Dayong] By the way,

456
00:27:25,600 --> 00:27:28,640
what did you say to Lu Xia?

457
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:34,200
[water trickling]

458
00:27:47,120 --> 00:27:48,240
[Lu Xia] I'm back.

459
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,400
Why are you so late?

460
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:51,480
You had a date?

461
00:27:51,560 --> 00:27:52,520
[Lu Xia] Mm-hm.

462
00:28:11,320 --> 00:28:13,320
[calm music]

463
00:28:13,760 --> 00:28:16,560
When you truly know
the reason why you play tennis,

464
00:28:17,520 --> 00:28:19,840
you'll have the ability
to overcome the obstacles.

465
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:22,760
You'll be stronger on the court.

466
00:28:37,240 --> 00:28:38,920
QI NA, LU XIANGQIAN,
ZHANG YUAN, ZHUO HAO

467
00:28:39,040 --> 00:28:39,920
[Coach Qi] Lu Xia.

468
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:41,960
Don't let Siyang down.

469
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:44,840
Surpass your father.

470
00:28:45,160 --> 00:28:46,080
[sighs]

471
00:28:48,560 --> 00:28:52,240
TWO DAYS BEFORE THE MUNICIPAL QUALIFYING

472
00:28:52,320 --> 00:28:53,160
[Qiao Chen groaning]

473
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:59,360
[sighs]
Why didn't Lu Xia and the captain come?

474
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:03,600
What's the problem?

475
00:29:04,000 --> 00:29:06,400
[Qiao Chen] Did they really get sick?

476
00:29:09,320 --> 00:29:12,360
[groans]
No. He can't be sick.

477
00:29:12,800 --> 00:29:16,080
I asked Mu today.
He said Lu Xia is doing well.

478
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:18,200
He doesn't seem sick.

479
00:29:18,280 --> 00:29:19,800
You are annoying.

480
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:26,840
Aren't you hurting?

481
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:28,440
Not a bit.

482
00:29:36,440 --> 00:29:38,120
Why are you trying to be brave?

483
00:29:38,720 --> 00:29:41,720
The X-ray shows that your injury

484
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,760
is much worse than last time.

485
00:29:44,560 --> 00:29:47,720
You must have overused
your hand these days.

486
00:29:48,760 --> 00:29:51,880
It caused a recurrence.

487
00:29:52,480 --> 00:29:55,680
As far as it goes,
how long will it take to recover?

488
00:29:56,360 --> 00:30:00,880
So far, your recovery
is not totally wasted.

489
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:06,480
But I can't help you if you don't listen.

490
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:19,200
[Xiangqian] Don't you have training?

491
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:21,400
You look so serious.

492
00:30:21,800 --> 00:30:22,960
Let's play.

493
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:26,160
Should I let you win?

494
00:30:26,520 --> 00:30:27,440
No.

495
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:31,960
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

496
00:30:33,320 --> 00:30:34,800
You still have a lot to work on.

497
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:36,280
[doctor] As a doctor,

498
00:30:37,120 --> 00:30:38,720
to prevent you from recurrence,

499
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:40,960
I need to know...

500
00:30:41,560 --> 00:30:44,360
why do you have to be like this?

501
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:49,680
[sighs deeply]

502
00:30:50,240 --> 00:30:51,120
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

503
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:52,600
[grunts]

504
00:30:54,320 --> 00:30:57,520
[panting]

505
00:30:57,600 --> 00:31:02,160
Our goal is not to follow the path
of our predecessors,

506
00:31:03,160 --> 00:31:05,760
but to create the players of this age,

507
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:08,440
and to be the new power of Chinese tennis.

508
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:09,480
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

509
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:13,760
Lu Xia, develop your own theory.

510
00:31:16,360 --> 00:31:17,320
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

511
00:31:22,520 --> 00:31:24,240
[Siyang] For this purpose,

512
00:31:26,800 --> 00:31:28,120
I have to use my hand.

513
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:34,200
I'll be stronger.

514
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:40,960
[Xiangqian] Somebody knows you well
in Yu Qing.

515
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:42,600
Who is he?

516
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:44,880
Who can inspire you so much?

517
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:59,960
Chief, this is my interview
with Lu Xiangqian.

518
00:32:05,800 --> 00:32:08,200
You don't have anything useful.

519
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:10,520
[chief editor]
Did you interview him or not?

520
00:32:10,600 --> 00:32:14,360
[Sha] I want to get information on Lu Xia
and the high school league from him.

521
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:15,680
I'm really confused.

522
00:32:16,080 --> 00:32:20,560
He is a former professional player
and you are a non-professional reporter.

523
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:22,800
How could you do such a boring interview?

524
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:24,360
What is the point?

525
00:32:24,800 --> 00:32:29,280
These kids
will be professional players someday.

526
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:30,760
By that time,

527
00:32:31,040 --> 00:32:33,240
we'll be the ones
who know the professionals best.

528
00:32:34,080 --> 00:32:35,880
[Sha sighs]

529
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:39,120
Chief, Lu Xia is awesome.

530
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:44,080
We must seize this opportunity
before he becomes famous.

531
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:49,160
I believe that Lu Xia
will be a famous player in no time.

532
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:51,000
You didn't want to interview them.

533
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:54,360
Now there is a Master Cup outside of town.

534
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:56,320
Will you go?

535
00:32:56,760 --> 00:33:01,160
I would like to handle
these future professionals first.

536
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:05,320
I'll change my plans
and report on the high school league.

537
00:33:06,320 --> 00:33:07,520
Fine.

538
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:09,720
Is that okay?

539
00:33:11,760 --> 00:33:12,960
