540
00:33:16,840 --> 00:33:20,600
THE DAY BEFORE THE MUNICIPAL QUALIFYING
GUO ZI HIGH SCHOOL

541
00:33:21,520 --> 00:33:23,000
MU SIYANG

542
00:33:25,120 --> 00:33:26,760
HE XINGLONG

543
00:33:28,880 --> 00:33:30,720
ZHUO YU
GUO ZI HIGH SCHOOL, PLAYER

544
00:33:30,800 --> 00:33:32,080
LU XIA

545
00:33:32,760 --> 00:33:34,640
[gasps]
He's a freshman?

546
00:33:35,080 --> 00:33:35,920
Mm-hm.

547
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:38,240
GUAN YUE
GUO ZI HIGH SCHOOL, PLAYER AND COACH

548
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:40,880
[Yue] We have to pay special attention
to this boy.

549
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:43,800
No freshman in Yu Qing

550
00:33:44,320 --> 00:33:46,400
has become a main player before.

551
00:33:48,760 --> 00:33:53,400
Even a tennis genius could be
an ordinary player at the beginning.

552
00:33:54,800 --> 00:33:55,800
[snickers]

553
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:56,840
[sighs]

554
00:33:59,560 --> 00:34:00,680
Why did you stop?

555
00:34:00,760 --> 00:34:01,960
Are there any other players?

556
00:34:02,480 --> 00:34:03,520
Mm-hm.

557
00:34:08,320 --> 00:34:09,400
ZHUO ZHI, TANG JIALE

558
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:11,880
Ah! Wait, go back.

559
00:34:15,600 --> 00:34:17,159
ZHUO ZHI

560
00:34:17,239 --> 00:34:18,480
[Yu] It’s destiny.

561
00:34:19,360 --> 00:34:23,880
You know, I'm only coming to this match
to beat him.

562
00:34:24,520 --> 00:34:25,440
No worries.

563
00:34:26,080 --> 00:34:29,080
I'll study their competition order

564
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:33,600
and ensure that
you will play against Zhuo Zhi.

565
00:34:33,679 --> 00:34:35,800
Thank you. I'll go ahead, then.

566
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:46,800
I want to play
against Zhuo Zhi's teammates.

567
00:34:48,360 --> 00:34:49,440
[snickers]

568
00:34:59,040 --> 00:35:01,480
GUO ZI HIGH SCHOOL

569
00:35:03,160 --> 00:35:06,280
NATIONAL HIGH SCHOOL TENNIS LEAGUE
MUNICIPAL QUALIFYING

570
00:35:06,360 --> 00:35:10,680
I'm at the park where
the municipal qualifying will be held.

571
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:15,440
The path behind me
is the only way to the court.

572
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:17,760
This is a round match.

573
00:35:18,200 --> 00:35:21,840
Every school takes turns
to play the other five.

574
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:26,560
It means that a team has to win...

575
00:35:26,640 --> 00:35:27,640
Three games.

576
00:35:29,440 --> 00:35:32,400
...win three games
to advance to the next round.

577
00:35:32,480 --> 00:35:36,240
And you must have a point ranking in...

578
00:35:36,320 --> 00:35:37,600
The top five.

579
00:35:38,400 --> 00:35:43,200
...the top five
to participate in the tournament.

580
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:46,440
We'll have an amazing match.

581
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:49,160
Which team will you support?

582
00:35:49,240 --> 00:35:52,480
-Yu Qing is bound to win.
-Come on, Yu Qing.

583
00:35:52,560 --> 00:35:55,160
These are two fans of Yu Qing.

584
00:35:55,240 --> 00:35:56,760
[chuckles]
They seem quite excited.

585
00:35:56,840 --> 00:35:58,680
-If you have a favorite team,
-[Xiuwen] Come on.

586
00:35:58,760 --> 00:36:00,640
please mention me
on our Weibo Monthly Tennis.

587
00:36:00,720 --> 00:36:02,560
-Mm-hm.
-I'm your reporter, Xiao Sha.

588
00:36:03,680 --> 00:36:05,360
[whispers]
Go away. Hurry.

589
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:06,800
[Xiuwen mumbles]

590
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:10,120
See you next time.

591
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:12,920
♪ Were flying all over
As my cudgel waved ♪

592
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:14,360
♪ I had no more time to look back ♪

593
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:16,200
♪ The only thing was left... ♪

594
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:17,960
