595
00:36:18,080 --> 00:36:20,880
♪ Why a victory ended with loneliness
The wind was sighing in the dream ♪

596
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:21,880
[Lu Xia groans]

597
00:36:23,560 --> 00:36:26,080
[groaning, panting]

598
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:31,480
[audience cheer from TV]

599
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,840
[Lu Xia grunting]

600
00:36:35,720 --> 00:36:37,160
Why didn't the alarm go off?

601
00:36:37,560 --> 00:36:39,360
[panting]

602
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:46,320
[tense music]

603
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:57,800
[tense music continues]

604
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:09,040
[scoffs]

605
00:37:12,680 --> 00:37:14,800
Where is Lu Xia? It's so late.

606
00:37:15,160 --> 00:37:17,480
Yes. Where is he?

607
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:20,920
All eight of us should enter before ten,

608
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:22,560
or else, we'll be disqualified.

609
00:37:25,760 --> 00:37:26,960
[gasps]

610
00:37:27,040 --> 00:37:29,640
I have a bad feeling.

611
00:37:31,720 --> 00:37:32,760
[sighs]

612
00:37:33,760 --> 00:37:35,480
-[Siyang] Mu.
-Huh?

613
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:37,000
Did you reach him?

614
00:37:39,200 --> 00:37:44,000
Yes. He said he went out early.

615
00:37:44,080 --> 00:37:48,360
He bumped into a pregnant woman
who was about to give birth

616
00:37:49,400 --> 00:37:51,080
and took her to the hospital.

617
00:37:51,160 --> 00:37:52,080
What?

618
00:37:52,560 --> 00:37:55,840
Lu Xia took a pregnant woman
to the hospital?

619
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:57,760
[scoffs]
Who would believe that?

620
00:38:03,680 --> 00:38:05,840
Anyway, we have to go in first.

621
00:38:06,320 --> 00:38:09,040
Baiyang, lend me your spare uniform.

622
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:15,840
No. 128, Yu Qing High School.
All eight players are here.

623
00:38:18,120 --> 00:38:19,480
[woman 1] Fine. Okay.

624
00:38:24,600 --> 00:38:26,600
[tense music]

625
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:34,680
LU XIA
CLASS 2, GRADE 10

626
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:45,960
You are that freshman main player, Lu Xia?

627
00:38:49,360 --> 00:38:51,360
[tense music]

628
00:38:52,280 --> 00:38:53,280
Come.

629
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:55,440
[woman 2] Come here.

630
00:38:58,880 --> 00:39:00,720
-Take your hands off.
-Off his face.

631
00:39:16,280 --> 00:39:17,240
[woman 1 chuckles]

632
00:39:18,440 --> 00:39:20,000
You are rather photogenic.

633
00:39:20,080 --> 00:39:21,960
[Tan Jiale and Qiao Chen sigh]

634
00:39:22,040 --> 00:39:24,080
[woman 2]
Freshmen can't usually compete here.

635
00:39:24,160 --> 00:39:25,240
I remember you.

636
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:27,720
[woman 2] You're pretty good. Good luck.

637
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:28,840
[sighs]

638
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:31,080
Here are your entry cards.

639
00:39:31,160 --> 00:39:32,080
[Yan Zhiming] Thanks.

640
00:39:33,240 --> 00:39:34,400
[laughs nervously]

641
00:39:38,320 --> 00:39:39,320
[Yan Zhiming] Let's go.

642
00:39:45,080 --> 00:39:46,200
[sighs]

643
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:48,240
Why am I lost again?

644
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:51,680
Where's the court?

645
00:39:53,560 --> 00:39:54,600
[Ying sighs]

646
00:39:57,080 --> 00:39:58,000
LITTLE NITWIT

647
00:39:58,080 --> 00:39:59,920
I'm truly a nitwit.

648
00:40:11,560 --> 00:40:12,520
[both gasp]

649
00:40:12,840 --> 00:40:14,600
-Ying.
-Sha.

650
00:40:14,680 --> 00:40:17,080
Where is the court?

651
00:40:17,160 --> 00:40:18,920
I've been looking for it for 20 minutes.

652
00:40:19,000 --> 00:40:21,680
Uh, I'm useless.

653
00:40:21,760 --> 00:40:23,240
It took me 30 minutes.

654
00:40:24,160 --> 00:40:27,640
Uh, let's look for it separately, okay?

655
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:29,480
Mm-hm.

656
00:40:29,560 --> 00:40:31,040
I'll look over there.

657
00:40:31,120 --> 00:40:32,320
Then I'll go this way.

658
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:33,320
-[Ying] Mm-hm.
-Mm-hm.

659
00:40:34,280 --> 00:40:35,720
[Sha sighs]

660
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:41,800
COURT 1 TO COURT 3
COURT 4 TO COURT 6

661
00:40:41,880 --> 00:40:43,480
[Mu] You still have a lot to work on.

662
00:40:45,160 --> 00:40:47,440
-You still have...
-Lu Xia.

663
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,280
weren't you still on the way?

664
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:51,240
You are quick. Why didn't you tell us?

665
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:52,960
[Mu chuckles]

666
00:40:53,040 --> 00:40:55,360
-Hm?
-[Mu] You still have a lot to work on.

667
00:40:57,640 --> 00:40:58,560
[Xiuwen gasps]

668
00:41:01,040 --> 00:41:02,840
Liu Xia, I'm talking to you.
Do you hear me?

669
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:05,040
-[shushes]
-Uh...

670
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:09,640
Mu.

671
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:12,960
I just signed up for Lu Xia.

672
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:15,320
-Oh.
-Oh.

673
00:41:18,320 --> 00:41:20,480
Mu, do me a favor.

674
00:41:21,160 --> 00:41:22,200
What?

675
00:41:24,160 --> 00:41:26,080
Let's go to a place with a lot of girls.

676
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:27,720
You'll pretend to be Lu Xia.

677
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:29,600
Pretend to be Lu Xia?

678
00:41:29,680 --> 00:41:31,440
-I...
-Just give it a try.

679
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:35,840
[clears throat]

680
00:41:36,520 --> 00:41:39,120
-[man 1] How's that trick?
-It still needs improvement.

681
00:41:39,200 --> 00:41:42,040
[imitating Lu Xia]
Those people still have a lot to work on.

682
00:41:44,640 --> 00:41:45,920
Try acting with more emotion.

683
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:48,080
[sighs]
More emotion?

684
00:41:49,200 --> 00:41:50,040
Mmm.

685
00:41:50,680 --> 00:41:54,360
-His serve, compared to my Twist Serve,
-[man 2 grunting]

686
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:56,000
is nothing.

687
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:57,960
You're good.

688
00:41:58,080 --> 00:42:00,080
-[chuckles]
-Again. Again.

689
00:42:02,600 --> 00:42:03,600
Senior,

690
00:42:04,080 --> 00:42:06,520
haven't you mastered the Eastern Grip?

691
00:42:07,080 --> 00:42:08,200
You are Lu Xia himself.

692
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:10,560
You're really feeling this, aren't you?

693
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:12,440
Hey.

694
00:42:12,840 --> 00:42:14,120
You can do the Twist Serve?

695
00:42:15,120 --> 00:42:16,160
[Mu] Of course.

696
00:42:16,560 --> 00:42:18,240
I'm a main player of Yu Qing.

697
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,760
I'm Lin Ke from Jin Qiu.

698
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:22,400
I want to see it for myself.

699
00:42:22,960 --> 00:42:24,640
Get up. Follow me.

700
00:42:24,720 --> 00:42:25,640
[sighs]

701
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:27,480
Uh...

702
00:42:28,440 --> 00:42:29,760
Is it necessary?

703
00:42:31,840 --> 00:42:32,920
[Sha sighs]

704
00:42:33,360 --> 00:42:34,920
[Sha] We have come full circle.

705
00:42:36,480 --> 00:42:39,600
Peng Xiang will come to pick us up
in ten minutes.

706
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:42,520
Call her again.

707
00:42:47,960 --> 00:42:48,880
[gasps]

708
00:42:48,960 --> 00:42:51,360
Look, isn't that Lu Xia?

709
00:42:52,760 --> 00:42:54,760
[upbeat music]

710
00:42:55,520 --> 00:42:56,640
It seems so.

711
00:42:56,720 --> 00:42:58,280
-Come on.
-Okay.

